author: Patrick Cc:
description:
The UFC is more profitable and mainstream than ever before.. but longtime fans can feel that something’s off. The sport now feels like it’s traded passion for profit. This video breaks down how Dana White’s obsession with Power Slap and the UFC’s new “content machine” model, may have pushed the organization into its darkest era yet.
